msgstr "Terminal"

#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:495(para)
msgid ""
"Specifies whether the command in the <literal>Exec</literal> key runs in a "
"terminal window. If the value is <literal>true</literal> the command runs in "
"a terminal window."
